Retrieve cadastral gaps around the PARCA

get_vides.Rd

Retrieve cadastral gaps around the PARCA

Usage

get_vides(x)

Arguments

x

An sf object used as the input area. It must contain a source field with bdp or etalab value.

Value

An sf object of type POLYGON containing cadastral gaps with standardized fields, including:

  • TYPE - Empty, to complete

  • NATURE - Empty

  • NAME - Empty, to complete

  • SOURCE - Empty
